<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 16:26:38 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a85bae93ee</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一棵橡树的大树枝上，一片橡树叶的小芽成为了焦点（本就该如此！）。光线如此戏剧化，吸引了我的目光。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="In the foreground, a large branch of an oak tree crosses the frame midway, horizontally. In the middle of the frame, on top of the branch, a little shoot of new oak leaves is bathed in a patch of sunlight like a spotlight, making it glow. The backdrop is dense foliage." height="1500" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/bsag/6a4a85bae93ee.webp" width="2000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://bsag.some.pics"&gt;@bsag&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 16:26:38 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>溪边旋花</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4a850d06c90</link><description>&lt;p&gt;小溪边的一些旋花。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="A patch of white, trumpet shaped Convolvulus flowers in the sun, near to a stream which can just been seen in the shade at the top right. The flowers are pointing towards the sun. Some are fully open, others closed, twisted like furled umbrellas." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/bsag/6a4a850d06c90.webp" width="1500"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://bsag.some.pics"&gt;@bsag&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 16:23:44 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a8421d2544</link><description>&lt;p&gt;夏天是我最不喜欢的季节，尤其是在热浪来袭的时候。大树投下的宜人阴凉是我的庇护所。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Looking up into the wavy, shady branches of a large tree. There is a glimpse of blue sky and a few light clouds beyond." height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/bsag/6a4a8421d2544.webp" width="1500"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://bsag.some.pics"&gt;@bsag&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 16:19:48 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>灰色日子里的色彩</title><link>https://some.pics/6a4a7d983acb6</link><description>&lt;p&gt;灰色日子的色彩。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Thistle blossoms, closeup. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a4a7d983acb6.jpg" width="1127"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 15:51:54 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a4a71c1ce893</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🏃🏻 完美的周日跑步&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🏃🏻 Perfect zondag loopje " height="1486" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/6a4a71c1ce893.jpg" width="1179"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 Jul 2026 15:01:24 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>